messages.messageBody:
These appeared on ManyPaths, thought others might be interested:

#1 -- Free Educational Video Tapes from Federal Reserve Bank of San
Francisco

<A
HREF="http://www.frbsf.org/education/curriculum/index.html">Student
Activities from the FRBSF</A>
http://www.frbsf.org/education/curriculum/index.html

#2 -- from another list

*****************************************

The Human Genome Project is offering a "multimedia kit" (The Human
Genome
Project: Exploring our Molecular Selves) developed for high school
students
and the general public. The kit includes a CD-ROM, an award winning
video
documentary, a poster, and a brochure about human genetics.

Full-Details from this 2/12/01 press release:
http://www.nhgri.nih.gov/NEWS/HGP_unveils_education_kit.html

Direct ordering info at:
http://www.nhgri.nih.gov/educationkit/

Lynda
If Ignorance Is Bliss Why Aren't More People Happy?
